{"tid":2340232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12港人案下週一開審 案件將以秘密審訊形式處理","createTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T02:24:48.000Z","uid":292499,"like":15,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"86d467a49643cd4b1edfd36ae65faf4795fea54e","tid":2340232,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"【12港人家屬譴責中國當局擬秘密審訊12人】<br />\n<br />\n12港人被秘密關押超過四個月，當中7人家屬今日突然收到由中國當局指派的「官派律師」通知，指其中10人將於12月28日星期一下午2時30分，以視像方式於深圳市鹽田區人民法院受審。另外2名於被捕時未滿18歲的港人，則會由檢察院聽證會處理，日期未知。<br />\n<br />\n12港人中，10人須面對審訊，但目前僅7人的家屬收到開庭通知。<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">鹽田法院回覆傳媒查詢時明言，12港人案件屬於「秘密案件」，將不允許公眾人士、記者等人旁聽，僅著家屬自行聯絡負責審訊的法官詢問能否旁聽。而在鹽田法院公佈的庭審直播時間表，亦未有列出10位港人的審訊。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於法院在審訊前3日才發出通知，當中包括公眾假期，家屬已無法趕及親自到法庭旁聽。對於中國當局將秘密審訊12港人，家屬予以強烈譴責 &mdash; 此做法完全漠視基本人權價值，亦違背中國對外宣傳之「陽光司法」原則。<br />\n<br />\n家屬在此向中國當局要求：<br />\n<br />\n&bull;  全程網絡視像直播庭審；<br />\n&bull;  向家屬及全港公眾公開12港人案件審訊詳情，包括兩位未成年人進行聽證的日期、庭審形式及法官資料等；<br />\n&bull;  公開庭審，讓家屬代表、家屬委託律師、香港及國際媒體、各國外交使節人員能到場旁聽；<br />\n&bull;  要求當局在審訊後對外公布判決書；及<br />\n&bull;  承諾若12港人最終被判監禁，家屬可盡快探望。<br />\n<br />\n另要求香港政府：<br />\n<br />\n&bull;  派員旁聽案件，確保12港人作為香港公民的權利得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n12港人家屬<br />\n2020年12月25日<br />\n<br />\n#save12hkyouths<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107761137730984/posts/227257632448000/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107761137730984%2Fposts%2F227257632448000%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=ff281b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107761137730984/posts/227257632448000/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c3c2e81171fde6b5aa59dae66bcc165b4d9398a8","tid":2340232,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"秘密審訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb542d8af30b4f52aa5d22e59ec289321ab93c41","tid":2340232,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4065382776bd948c7d8fbe58e347ba9255a733","tid":2340232,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bef08500194f0b416e63b0ae0cc9aa493ee6ad","tid":2340232,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb542d8af30b4f52aa5d22e59ec289321ab93c41","tid":2340232,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc88dcc85f69db648d74f4aa6d075a29f27b502","tid":2340232,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e4065382776bd948c7d8fbe58e347ba9255a733","tid":2340232,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i